      "text": "えっ、琴乃ちゃん？\nしー、って……レッスン室に誰かいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Kotono-chan?\nShh…? Is someone in the lesson room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9666659673,
