      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 373.0333063762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "えぇぇぇ！？　なになに！？\nお父さん？　お母さん？　その箱って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh?! What is this?!\nDad? Mom? That box is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 373.366644478,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.328564800002,
          "startTime": 378.8999730428
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 378.5333063762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～～～～～～！！\n魚魚っとさんの抱きまくらだ～～～～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~~~~~~!\nIt’s a GyoGyotto-san printed long cushion~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.6656338696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 386.6989570305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、みんなで用意してみたの\n星見市の広報の方からも、許可をいただいてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ we all prepared it together.\nWe even got permission from the Hoshimi City public relations department.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 390.4000062943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "さくらが感謝を伝えたいように\n私達も、さくらに感謝を伝えたかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as you wanted to express your gratitude‚\nwe also wanted to express ours to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 396.9338774845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 400.8671945417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになった日から……ううん、出会った日から\nずっとずっと、ありがとう。さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since you became an idol… no‚ ever since we met‚\nas always‚ thank you. Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 407.1005502546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 411.3005095645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、遙子ちゃん……お父さん、お母さん……\nスタッフさんも……感謝するのは私の方なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ Haruko-chan… Dad‚ Mom…\nAnd everyone on the staff… I’m the one who should be grateful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 419.0338652774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 426.0338428978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr026.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ありがとう……みんな、ありがとう……！\n一生の思い出だよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… thank you… Thank you everyone…!\nThis is a memory I'll cherish forever…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 433.400531944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "（私は一人じゃ、ここまで来れなかった）\n（昔も、今も、沢山の人に元気をもらってるから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I couldn’t have come this far by myself.）\n（Since many people have encouraged me‚ both in the past and present‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 443.6338835879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr028.m4a",
      "text": "（辛い時も、大変な時もあるけど、また頑張れる）\n（だから私も、みんなに元気をあげたい。笑顔にしたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（although there are tough and difficult times‚ I can keep going.）\n（So‚ I also want to give everyone my energy. I want to make them smile.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 457.0338896914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr029.m4a",
      "text": "（どうかこの想いが、空の向こうまで届きますように）\n（――私、『アイドル』に出会えて、とっても幸せです）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I hope this feeling reaches beyond the sky.）\n（――I’m so happy to have become an “idol”.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 470.7005319439,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
